      <title>国际货币基金组织理事会改变贷款规则以加速债务重组</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/imf-board-changes-lending-rules-to-speed-up-debt-restructuring</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国际货币基金组织执行董事会投票决定改革其支持债务重组的程序，允许债务重组计划在债权人抵制的情况下继续推进。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/imf-board-changes-lending-rules-to-speed-up-debt-restructuring</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 18:07:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍威尔表示通胀意外后将推迟降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/powell-signals-high-rates-for-longer-due-to-persistent-inflation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔表示，在一系列令人惊讶的高通胀数据之后，政策制定者降息的时间将比之前预期的要长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/powell-signals-high-rates-for-longer-due-to-persistent-inflation</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 17:38:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
